org.apache.gora.query.impl.ResultBase

  • Packages that use ResultBase 
    Package Description
    org.apache.gora.accumulo.query
    This package contains all the Accumulo store query representation class as well as Result set representing class when query is executed over the Accumulo dataStore.
    org.apache.gora.avro.query
    This package contains a query representation class for Avro as well as Result set representing class when query is executed.
    org.apache.gora.cassandra.query
    This package contains all the Cassandra store query representation class as well as Result set representing class when query is executed over the Cassandra dataStore.
    org.apache.gora.couchdb.query
    This package contains all the CouchDB store query representation class as well as Result set representing class when query is executed over the CouchDB dataStore.
    org.apache.gora.hbase.query
    This package contains all the HBase store query representation class as well as Result set representing class when query is executed over the HBase dataStore.
    org.apache.gora.infinispan.query
    This package contains all the Infinispan store query representation class as well as Result set representing class when query is executed over the Infinispan dataStore.
    org.apache.gora.jcache.query
    This package contains all the JCache store query representation class as well as Result set representing class when query is executed over the JCache dataStore.
    org.apache.gora.memory.store
    This package contains memory based DataStore implementation for tests.
    org.apache.gora.mongodb.query
    This package contains all the MongoDB store query representation class as well as Result set representing class when query is executed over the MongoDB dataStore.
    org.apache.gora.solr.query
